description: Step into luxury with this spacious condo in a South Boston brownstone a short distance from the vibrant Seaport District. This beautifully renovated, open-concept, two-bedroom and two-bathroom condo is a testament to luxury. The highest quality is evident in every detail, from the two full-tile/quartz marble bathrooms to the stunning granite and stainless open kitchen. The gas fireplace, custom moldings, private rear deck off the master, in-unit laundry, high ceilings, ample built-in closets/shelving, and exposed brick all contribute to the luxurious feel. With its proximity to the bustling Seaport District and excellent restaurants and shops (including Foodie's), this home embodies luxury. A quick walk to the T and no. 9 bus puts you minutes from downtown and Copley Square.
